    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <i>What Comes Next</i> 中，你将扮演索菲（Sophie），一位生活在1970年代法国的小女孩。与你最好的朋友兼宠物老鼠阿米（Ami）一起，你必须逃离邪恶的孤儿院，踏上旅程寻找你的父母，并通过解谜和潜行来完成任务。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一起解谜：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了通过某些区域，你需要在索菲和阿米之间切换，利用它们各自的独特能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167320/extras/9773f3ea768ecbc2a15cc093601537d3.poster.avif?t=1748533886\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167320/extras/9773f3ea768ecbc2a15cc093601537d3.webm?t=1748533886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167320/extras/9773f3ea768ecbc2a15cc093601537d3.mp4?t=1748533886\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >躲避敌人：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将面对多个敌人：守卫、狗、猫，以及邪恶的孤儿院管理员克鲁艾尔（Cruéll）！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167320/extras/7e9d5995a380b491d1552eda91c29b17.poster.avif?t=1748533886\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167320/extras/7e9d5995a380b491d1552eda91c29b17.webm?t=1748533886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167320/extras/7e9d5995a380b491d1552eda91c29b17.mp4?t=1748533886\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扮演阿米：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿米体型小巧而敏捷，能够钻进狭窄的缝隙，跳过障碍物，并找到对索菲有用的物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167320/extras/a4f73f2cf7a52a57c88ed9caba8f52c6.poster.avif?t=1748533886\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167320/extras/a4f73f2cf7a52a57c88ed9caba8f52c6.webm?t=1748533886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167320/extras/a4f73f2cf7a52a57c88ed9caba8f52c6.mp4?t=1748533886\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事背景：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <i>What Comes Next</i> 中，你将扮演索菲，一个生活在由残暴管理员掌管的孤儿院里的女孩。你的唯一朋友是聪明忠诚的小老鼠阿米。你们必须一起逃离孤儿院，踏上冒险旅程寻找索菲的父母。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你需要在索菲和阿米之间切换，通过解谜、躲避敌人，并在城市中寻找关于索菲身世的线索。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >   <br>游戏特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 游戏采用独特的美术风格，配有优美的音乐和音效，拥有多个有趣的探索区域，并隐藏着一个等待揭开的神秘故事。准备好和你的小老鼠一起踏上这场神奇的冒险，探索 <i>What Comes Next</i> 吧！</p>",
